sentences.english: Disqualifications - An all white dog or a dog with no white.
sentences.chinese: 任何全白的狗或沒有白色的狗都屬於失格。

sentences.english: Undershot or overshot bite is a disqualification.
sentences.chinese: 上顎或下顎突出爲失格。

sentences.english: A distinctly long coat is a disqualification.
sentences.chinese: 明顯過長的被毛屬於失格。

sentences.english: Short, smooth coat on both head and legs is a disqualification.
sentences.chinese: 頭部和腿部的被毛短而平滑屬於失格。

sentences.english: Black-and-tan or liver color to be disqualified.
sentences.chinese: 黑色帶褐色斑紋或肝色屬於失格。

sentences.english: Undershot or Overshot bites are a disqualification.
sentences.chinese: 上鄂突出或下鄂突出的咬合都是失格。

sentences.english: White extending on the shoulders or neck is a disqualification.
sentences.chinese: 白色延伸到肩胛或頸部屬於失格。

sentences.english: Ears hanging as on a hound, or semi-prick ears are disqualifications .
sentences.chinese: 耳朵象獵犬那樣耷拉着或半立耳都屬於失格。
